Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:05.18,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家来此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.90,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不分你我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:10.16,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}瞬间新生的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:14.20,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论何地  不曾改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:17.86,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}oh  yeah yeah yeah
